    "The dataset belonging to these images contains 1.686.353 separate cell location information [56].Different types of cells vary in size, density, and shape.",
    "In particular, Shsy5y with long protrusions and overlapping cells has the lowest segmentation success.",
    "Therefore, the SCIS dataset focused on these challenges had been created.",
    "There are three different types of neuronal cells in the SCIS dataset, namely Cortical neurons (Cort), Shsy5y, and Astrocyte (Astro).",
    "Statistical properties of this cell information are presented in Table 3 [57]."
